  Note: We intentionally DON'T load product.js here because:
  1. Our section-replo-buy-box.js imports renderSwatches directly from TS
  2. product.js contains global SMP initializers that can conflict
  3. This ensures we use the current v2 API instead of potentially cached v1
{%- endcomment -%}
